  textArray:
  - This companion boosts your strength in combat.
  - This companion doubles the value of the coins you pick up.
  - This companion reduces the amount of damage you take in battle.
  - This companion makes you immune to taking damage from fire.
  - This companion increases your life power and constantly heals your wounds.
  - This companion makes you immune to being frozen.
  - This companion will fetch items that drop from enemies.
  - This companion will run towards and attack enemies in your path.
  - This companion makes you move faster than you could before.
  - This companion will make potions when an enemy is killed.
  - This companion will shoot pellets at enemies in your path.
  - This companion will make you immune from being stunned.
  - This companion will shoot pellets that stun your enemies.
  - This companion will increase the rate at which you grow stronger.
  - 'I know the creatures of this land, bring one to me and I will share what I know.

    When you get new companions your old ones will return here.'
